headline: This CEO said no to a 15-year wait for his dream job. He took the fast track instead: ‘I don’t have that much time’
summary: Get Digital's CEO was once offered a 15-year path to the C-suite, so he walked. He now leads the $17.8 billion cybersecurity firm.
